==== ENTRY 1 ====
HEADWORD: Telegraph plant
<hw>Telegraph plant</hw> <fld>(Bot.)</fld>, <def>A tick trefoil
(<spn>Meibomia gyrans</spn> formerly <spn>Desmodium gyrans</spn>),
native of the East Indies; it is a leguminous plant whose lateral
leaflets jerk up and down like the arms of a semaphore, and also rotate
on their axes.</def>⟦br⟧
[<source>Webster 1913 Suppl.</source>]</p>

<p><ent>Telegraphone</ent>⟦br⟧
